@startuml main_thread
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "DejaVu Sans"
title Wątek główny i metoda currentThread()

participant "JVM Launch" as JVM
participant "main thread\n(Thread.currentThread())" as MAIN
participant "Worker Thread" as W

JVM -> MAIN : tworzy i startuje
note right of MAIN
  Thread.currentThread()
    .getName()     : "main"
    .getId()       : systemowe ID
    .getPriority() : 5 (NORM)
    .isDaemon()    : false
    .getState()    : RUNNABLE
end note

MAIN -> W : new Thread(...).start()
activate W
MAIN -> MAIN : Thread.sleep(ms) → TIMED_WAITING
W --> MAIN : notify / join
MAIN <-- W : run() zakończony
deactivate W

MAIN -> MAIN : zakończenie main()\n→ JVM kończy się\n  (gdy brak user threads)

@enduml

